The advertisement showed a woman appearing in her mid twenties commenting on her choice of an outdoor furniture set. Located behind her is a four piece set of wicker outdoor chairs with plush grey cushions. The ad looks very appealing because the furniture is well staged outside so it makes it easy to imagine owning the set or one that is very similar. The woman in the ad also looks very happy with her purchase which encourages me to look into it as well.
